details.summary: Mark Stu is a certified PMP who has been managing projects for over two decades, including managing the IBM Watson project and the construction of the International Space Station

Emily is a natural leader with a master's degree in social work; she brings in more than 8 years of experience in coordinating launch campaigns for products of major brands like Nike, Nestle, and Nokia

Barbara is a website and physical product designer and illustrator with more than 5 years of experience. She received her bachelor's in graphic design from the University of moscow, and worked for 2 years as lead graphic designer for the website of the Hilton hotel in Moscow

Steve is a fullstack developer with 5 years of experience. Having worked as a freelancer for the past three consecutive years, Steve is familiar with several programming languages and frameworks, including Python, PHP, Node.js, JavaScript, Angular, Django, and a few others
